				"type": "Summary",
				"ordinal": "1"
			},
			{
				"text": "\n            Man in the middle\n        ",
				"title": "Impact",
				"type": "General",
				"ordinal": "2"
			},
			{
				"text": "\n            FortiGate with the SSLVPN web portal feature configured.\n        ",
				"title": "Affected Products",
				"type": "General",
				"ordinal": "3"
			},
			{
				"text": "\n            Upgrade to FortiOS 5.0.13 / 5.2.6 / 5.4.0 Ã‚ As a workaround the SSLVPN web portal can be disabled\n        ",
